I don't know why people like using huge sig pics everytime they post, especially more than once in the same topic, boards are laggy eough as it is.  Set default option for [] Including custom sig to no as deafult maybe and use it in first post in thread, not every single one.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  3) Signatures must be kept below 50kb in size. Flash/shockwave animations are allowed, as long as they are below this size. Remember, not everyone is on broadband.<br>
<br>
4) Scripts that produce 'mouse-over' graphical effects on images in signatures are not allowed, as they have been proven to cause problems for some users.<br>
<br>
5) A signature should be no deeper than 10 lines of text, including images, and should not be so wide as to cause the window to extend on a 800x600 display.<br>
